OL,3,CCardiff University to scale down music
OL,4,Cand languages degrees but scrap others
OL,6,FThat new school would continue to
OL,7,Foffer undergraduate and postgraduate
OL,8,Fmusic degree programmes, but with
OL,9,Frevised entry targets and content,
OL,10,Fwhile also continuing its offering of
OL,11,Fmodern languages programmes, but to
OL,12,Fsmaller cohorts and primarily in
OL,13,FFrench, Spanish, Mandarin and Japanese.
OL,15,FBut degrees in ancient history, and
OL,16,Freligion and theology, would come to
OL,17,Fan end after students enrolling this
OL,18,FSeptember for 2025-26 complete their
OL,19,Fcourses.
