OL,3,CCardiff University to scale down music
OL,4,Cand languages degrees but scrap others
OL,6,F"We will of course continue to offer
OL,7,Four current set of degree programmes
OL,8,Ffor 2025-26 and are committed to
OL,9,Fteaching all students entering next
OL,10,FSeptember until the completion of
OL,11,Ftheir degree in these subjects."
OL,13,FAddressing staff, the vice-chancellor
OL,14,Facknowledged the "anxiety that the
OL,15,FAcademic Future project has created
OL,16,Ffor many of you, and I hope that
OL,17,Ftoday's announcement brings some
OL,18,Freassurance. There is much work yet to
OL,19,Fbe done to realise the ambitions of
OL,20,Fthis new School, and I hope you will
OL,21,Ffeel able to play a part in this."
