OL,3,CCardiff University to scale down music
OL,4,Cand languages degrees but scrap others
OL,6,FProfessor Larner added that the new
OL,7,FSchool of Global Humanities would seek
OL,8,Fto expand the university's translation
OL,9,Fdegree provision, continue to offer
OL,10,FLanguages for All "with the languages
OL,11,Foffered there shaped by student
OL,12,Fdemand", and develop a "new suite of
OL,13,Fdegree programmes to fulfil the
OL,14,Fambitions of the new School `
OL,15,Fchallenge-oriented, inclusive, co-
OL,16,Fcreated and committed to advancing the
OL,17,FPublic Humanities agenda".
OL,19,FThe new proposal will now be put to
OL,20,FUniversity Council on 17 June for its
OL,21,Fapproval.
