OL,3,CCardiff University to scale down music
OL,4,Cand languages degrees but scrap others
OL,6,Fat Cardiff University, said: "It is
OL,7,Fgood to see the University Executive
OL,8,FBoard, under pressure from our
OL,9,Fmembers' massive public campaign to
OL,10,Fsave jobs, has now agreed to reverse
OL,11,Fits initial plans to cut nursing,
OL,12,Fmusic, and modern languages provision
OL,13,Fentirely.
OL,15,F"However, it is unacceptable that
OL,16,Fmanagement continue to keep more than
OL,17,F400 staff in scope for redundancy with
OL,18,Fno end in sight. The physical and
OL,19,Fmental health effects of this are
OL,20,Fbecoming unbearable for many of our
OL,21,Fmembers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
