OL,3,CCardiff University to scale down music
OL,4,Cand languages degrees but scrap others
OL,6,F"We will continue to press university
OL,7,Fleaders in the strongest terms to take
OL,8,Fall staff out of scope for redundancy
OL,9,Fand to work with us to find ways to
OL,10,Fcontinue teaching and research in
OL,11,Fancient history, languages, religion,
OL,12,Fand theology.
OL,14,F"As we have argued from the start, no
OL,15,Fredundancies would be needed at all if
OL,16,Fthe university was willing to reduce
OL,17,Fits overly ambitious and self-imposed
OL,18,Ffinancial targets and draw on its vast
OL,19,Fsums of accessible cash to fund a
OL,20,Flonger recovery period.
